      "span_text": "I agree with the conclusions by Wasenang et al. that their findings suggest that the application of serum cfDNA methylation assays offer a promising alternative to the more invasive methods currently considered necessary to secure a diagnosis of cholangiocarcinoma [CITATION_1] ."
